fields.value:
> <#731845822227939338>
This channel lets you know which webtoons are updating every day!

> <#730531385667747842>
You can discuss any webtoon here!

> <#753791338897604658>
Read pins! For collaborations, please use DMs to contact to avoid conversations in chat and the ads being flooded over. 

> <#732618737441570835>
You can promote yourself here. Feel free to share your webtoons or social media, but **no** servers please.
